    <item>
      <title>随着经济复苏，德国投资者信心大增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/german-investor-confidence-jumps-as-economic-recovery-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者对德国经济的信心连续第十个月上升——反映出人们对经济增长在一年多的近乎停滞后正在恢复的乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/german-investor-confidence-jumps-as-economic-recovery-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 09:08:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非部长在反对必和必拓收购后对英美资源集团的计划表示欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/south-africa-minister-warms-to-anglo-plan-after-opposing-bhp-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 拒绝必和必拓集团 (BHP Group) 的两项提议后，宣布计划将其铂金业务分拆，作为重大改组的一部分，南非矿业部长采取了和解的语气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/south-africa-minister-warms-to-anglo-plan-after-opposing-bhp-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 09:06:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国就业市场降温，英国央行继续降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/uk-unemployment-rate-rises-to-highest-since-last-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国失业率上升，私营部门工资增长放缓，这些迹象表明劳动力市场普遍降温，这可能会让英国央行更有信心在未来几个月降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/uk-unemployment-rate-rises-to-highest-since-last-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
